Transport
  - Announce queue with rate limiting
  - Path expiry and table culling
  - Packet caching
  - Tunnel support
  - Path request/response protocol (request_path API)

Link
  - RTT measurement
  - Keepalive and watchdog timeouts
  - Link teardown negotiation
  - Ratchets (forward secrecy key rotation)
  - Establishment rate/cost metrics

Missing protocol features
  - IFAC (per-interface HMAC auth codes)
  - Channel (multiplexed channels over Link)
  - Buffer (streaming buffer over Channel)
  - Resource hash verification of assembled payload

Firmware
  - BLE long-lived connection drops in RNS wrapper (upstream RNS issue, our side holds 120s+)
  - Channel stats commands (CMD_STAT_CHTM, CMD_STAT_PHYPRM) - RNS polls these periodically
  - rnodeconf ROM/EEPROM read support
  - RAK3172 / STM32WLE5 port (Cortex-M4F HAL, different toolchain)
  - Light sleep with proper OLED decoupling for field deployment
New capabilities
  - LXMF propagation node (standalone store-and-forward on MCU)
  - LXMF delivery endpoint (receive messages on MCU without host)
